*=======================================================================

  DATA:

  lr_sr_bom                TYPE REF TO /scwm/cl_sr_bom,
  lr_log                   TYPE REF TO /scwm/cl_log,

  ls_bo_tu_new             TYPE /scwm/s_bo_tu_new.


